OL,3,C'One day his heart just stopped':
OL,4,Cwidow pushes for more health checks
OL,6,FA woman is urging everyone to get
OL,7,Fthemselves checked for underlying
OL,8,Fheart problems after her husband's
OL,9,Fsudden death.
OL,11,FBlanca Palacin's partner Neil Hussey
OL,12,Fdied in 2015, aged 40, after his heart
OL,13,Fstopped while out on a bike ride.
OL,15,FBlanca says there were no signs of
OL,16,FNeil having any heart condition and he
OL,17,Flived an active lifestyle.
OL,19,FShe explained: "Neil was a very fit
OL,20,Fperson, he was a swimmer, a runner, a
OL,21,Fcyclist.
