OL,3,C'One day his heart just stopped':
OL,4,Cwidow pushes for more health checks
OL,6,F"He went out with his bike one day and
OL,7,Fhis heart just stopped. No warnings,
OL,8,Fno second chance.
OL,10,F"Losing someone who is so important to
OL,11,Fyou with no notice is dreadful for me
OL,12,Fas his wife, for his children. We
OL,13,Fdon't want anybody to go through that."
OL,15,FBlanca decided to set up the Neil
OL,16,FHussey Heart Charity in her late
OL,17,Fhusband's name to make sure others
OL,18,Fhave the opportunity to get checked
OL,19,Fbefore it is too late.
