OL,3,C'One day his heart just stopped':
OL,4,Cwidow pushes for more health checks
OL,6,FThe group is visiting local schools
OL,7,Fand clubs to give young people free
OL,8,Ftests.
OL,10,FThey use portable devices which take a
OL,11,Ffew seconds to monitor someone's heart
OL,12,Fand can give an early indication that
OL,13,Fsomething might be wrong.
OL,15,FBlanca added: "There are so many heart
OL,16,Fconditions that have no symptoms.
OL,17,FThere is an opportunity here to save
OL,18,Flives."
