OL,3,C'One day his heart just stopped':
OL,4,Cwidow pushes for more health checks
OL,6,FHeart disease remains one of the most
OL,7,Fcommon single causes of death across
OL,8,Fthe Channel Islands, with one in three
OL,9,Fpeople in Jersey affected by a
OL,10,Fcardiovascular issue.
OL,12,FJersey Consultant Cardiologist Andrew
OL,13,FMitchell said: "The incidents of most
OL,14,Fheart conditions are rising, the
OL,15,Fnumber of people we treat is going up
OL,16,F7-10% per year."
